Installation of backupuser:
=============================
To install backupuser simply run "make install" as root.
Running the install target will copy the files:
backupuser and bu_check_files to /usr/local/bin and install the manpages
backupuser.1 and bu_check_files.1 in /usr/local/man/man1

Deinstalling backupuser:
=============================
To deinstall backupuser run "make deinstall" as root.
